{"tid":975771,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"法國擬禁蒙面示威　梁振英：旺角暴亂後香港也沒禁止　「反對派」批一國兩制限制自由有根據嗎？","createTime":"2019-01-10T02:28:19.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-10T02:41:43.000Z","uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":11,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"f129cb35a5dcb12ae5538bcafe9e58fa2c66d023","tid":975771,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-10T02:28:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20190109/s00001/ed64d70ef4ffdcd8f16685ada89ed658.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20190109%2Fs00001%2Fed64d70ef4ffdcd8f16685ada89ed658.jpg&h=52d993e5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n針對有失控迹象的「黃背心」示威活動，法國總理菲利普周一（7日）公布，計劃禁止民眾參與未經政府批准的示威，示威者亦不可戴口罩。全國政協副主席、前特首梁振英今早在社交網站發帖評論有關報道，借此反駁民主派「『一國兩制』下香港自由受限」一說。<br />\n<br />\n梁振英在帖文中，引用《文匯報》今日一篇題為〈法遏「黃背心」集會禁蒙面〉報道，指：「法國是世界最崇尚自由的國家，在旺角暴亂後，香港也沒有禁止蒙面參加集會，反對派竟然經常說在『一國兩制』下香港的自由受到限制，有根據嗎？」<br />\n<br />\n工聯會立法會議員郭偉强在帖文下留言，稱同意梁振英的說法，又認為：「如果不違法，又和平，絕對不需要蒙面。通常蒙面，都係有預謀違法的第一步。」<br />\n<br />\n國家主席習近平上周三（2日）在《告台灣同胞書》發表40周年紀念會上表明「祖國必須統一，也必然統一」，並首度提出探索「一國兩制台灣方案」。台灣總統蔡英文早前與國際媒體茶敘時，便重申北京當局把「九二共識」重新定義為「一個中國、一國兩制」，這個名詞已不再有模糊空間，呼籲全台各政黨不要再講「九二共識」。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/ins/%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E/article/20190109/s00001/1547016066203/%E6%B3%95%E5%9C%8B%E6%93%AC%E7%A6%81%E8%92%99%E9%9D%A2%E7%A4%BA%E5%A8%81-%E6%A2%81%E6%8C%AF%E8%8B%B1-%E6%97%BA%E8%A7%92%E6%9A%B4%E4%BA%82%E5%BE%8C%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E4%B9%9F%E6%B2%92%E7%A6%81%E6%AD%A2-%E5%8F%8D%E5%B0%8D%E6%B4%BE%E6%89%B9%E4%B8%80%E5%9C%8B%E5%85%A9%E5%88%B6%E9%99%90%E5%88%B6%E8%87%AA%E7%94%B1%E6%9C%89%E6%A0%B9%E6%93%9A%E5%97%8E\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E8%2581%259E%2Farticle%2F20190109%2Fs00001%2F1547016066203%2F%25E6%25B3%2595%25E5%259C%258B%25E6%2593%25AC%25E7%25A6%2581%25E8%2592%2599%25E9%259D%25A2%25E7%25A4%25BA%25E5%25A8%2581-%25E6%25A2%2581%25E6%258C%25AF%25E8%258B%25B1-%25E6%2597%25BA%25E8%25A7%2592%25E6%259A%25B4%25E4%25BA%2582%25E5%25BE%258C%25E9%25A6%2599%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E4%25B9%259F%25E6%25B2%2592%25E7%25A6%2581%25E6%25AD%25A2-%25E5%258F%258D%25E5%25B0%258D%25E6%25B4%25BE%25E6%2589%25B9%25E4%25B8%2580%25E5%259C%258B%25E5%2585%25A9%25E5%2588%25B6%25E9%2599%2590%25E5%2588%25B6%25E8%2587%25AA%25E7%2594%25B1%25E6%259C%2589%25E6%25A0%25B9%25E6%2593%259A%25E5%2597%258E&d=8KJcfkCxAQ0n1%2B5enJZKwXIou9iuErJt32EjuWI86Zw%3D&h=e75ed103\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E8%2581%259E%2Farticle%2F20190109%2Fs00001%2F1547016066203%2F%25E6%25B3%2595%25E5%259C%258B%25E6%2593%25AC%25E7%25A6%2581%25E8%2592%2599%25E9%259D%25A2%25E7%25A4%25BA%25E5%25A8%2581-%25E6%25A2%2581%25E6%258C%25AF%25E8%258B%25B1-%25E6%2597%25BA%25E8%25A7%2592%25E6%259A%25B4%25E4%25BA%2582%25E5%25BE%258C%25E9%25A6%2599%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E4%25B9%259F%25E6%25B2%2592%25E7%25A6%2581%25E6%25AD%25A2-%25E5%258F%258D%25E5%25B0%258D%25E6%25B4%25BE%25E6%2589%25B9%25E4%25B8%2580%25E5%259C%258B%25E5%2585%25A9%25E5%2588%25B6%25E9%2599%2590%25E5%2588%25B6%25E8%2587%25AA%25E7%2594%25B1%25E6%259C%2589%25E6%25A0%25B9%25E6%2593%259A%25E5%2597%258E&h=b961a0a9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.mingpao.com/ins/%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E/article/20190109/s00001/1547016066203/%E6%B3%95%E5%9C%8B%E6%93%AC%E7%A6%81%E8%92%99%E9%9D%A2%E7%A4%BA%E5%A8%81-%E6%A2%81%E6%8C%AF%E8%8B%B1-%E6%97%BA%E8%A7%92%E6%9A%B4%E4%BA%82%E5%BE%8C%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E4%B9%9F%E6%B2%92%E7%A6%81%E6%AD%A2-%E5%8F%8D%E5%B0%8D%E6%B4%BE%E6%89%B9%E4%B8%80%E5%9C%8B%E5%85%A9%E5%88%B6%E9%99%90%E5%88%B6%E8%87%AA%E7%94%B1%E6%9C%89%E6%A0%B9%E6%93%9A%E5%97%8E</a>"},{"pid":"f2a6b11b8fea1c8576c5c60f342742e7cf9dbbe4","tid":975771,"uid":61832,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-10T02:34:29.000Z","msg":"無限制啊<br />\n<br />\n不過你條撚樣玩秋後算賬咁囉"},{"pid":"f4811952a91d7466e865689b0d43908e3306083c","tid":975771,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-10T02:41:43.000Z","msg":"用旺角同巴黎比<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  個腦生喺邊?"}]}